♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,980
= Episode 40 =

20
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:34,980
Your father sent someone to appoint

21
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:37,580
you as the crown prince,

22
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:41,100
praising you’ve been suffering for all the people.

23
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:44,420
The eunuch issuing the decree

24
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:45,460
was driven out by me.

25
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:48,580
I told him to let your father know

26
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:52,420
that I do not want you to be the crown prince,

27
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:55,900
or suffer for the people.

28
00:01:57,300 --> 00:01:58,420
You are so young.

29
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:04,420
This is the first time I

30
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,460
disobeyed him.

31
00:02:09,180 --> 00:02:10,300
I promise,

32
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:13,460
as long as you get better,

33
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,620
I’ll not make you be any crown prince,

34
00:02:20,580 --> 00:02:21,460
or learn

35
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:22,980
so many books by sages.

36
00:02:24,980 --> 00:02:26,820
You won’t live the same life as your father,

37
00:02:27,900 --> 00:02:28,860
toilsome and exhausted.

38
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:35,100
I will take you to catch crickets

39
00:02:36,180 --> 00:02:38,540
and flying cricket every day. How about that?

40
00:02:45,660 --> 00:02:46,340
Xinhe.

41
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,300
Your Highness,

42
00:02:58,300 --> 00:02:59,780
I know I’m being willful.

43
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:02,980
I know it’s wrong,

44
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:08,260
but I’m Zuixinglai’s mother.

45
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:14,940
Usually, I tried to be sensible,

46
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:20,100
to put the people in mind,

47
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,740
like His Majesty and Your Highness.

48
00:03:23,020 --> 00:03:24,580
But I failed in the end.

49
00:03:26,820 --> 00:03:27,740
Silly talk.

50
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:31,260
What’s the crime of you when you only do
what a mother will do for her child?

51
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:35,340
In fact, His Majesty…

52
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,020
Your Highness,

53
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:40,460
Zuixinglai is only a child.

54
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:44,100
He can’t shoulder the country,

55
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:45,380
and the people.

56
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:48,140
He is definitely not the sage emperor of Song

57
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:49,740
chosen by heaven.

58
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:52,740
He’s just my little darling,

59
00:03:57,740 --> 00:03:59,220
who can’t live without me.

60
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:02,860
Anyway, wherever he goes, I’ll follow.

61
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:04,140
I’ll be at any place where he is.

62
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:15,500
Xinhe,

63
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:19,500
Huirou…

64
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:23,340
Huirou has caught a fever.

65
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:31,300
Huirou is sick.

66
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:34,420
But it doesn’t seem to be pestilence.

67
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:35,700
She will be fine for sure.

68
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:38,900
Now that you’re

69
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:40,380
taking care of Zuixinglai personally.

70
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:43,540
You shall not take care of Huirou now.

71
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:47,740
Don’t worry.

72
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,420
I have checked her already.

73
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:52,620
I told her

74
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:55,100
that you were taking care of Zuixinglai.

75
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:56,500
But surely you would not

76
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:57,740
leave her alone.

77
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:02,580
Xinhe,

78
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:10,380
no matter how much she loves me or respects me,

79
00:05:13,140 --> 00:05:14,060
now,

80
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:19,660
she only needs His Majesty and you.

81
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:25,500
I’m willing to look after her for her entire life,

82
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,380
and treat her

83
00:05:27,380 --> 00:05:28,260
as my own daughter.

84
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:30,380
I have no child.

85
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:32,420
She is

86
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:33,460
the dearest in my heart.

87
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:34,820
You don’t worry about this,

88
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:41,620
yet in Huirou’s heart,

89
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:46,220
you’re everything to her.

90
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:49,900
No one can replace you.

91
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:54,780
And not only for her,

92
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:00,420
even for His Majesty,

93
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:05,540
you’re irreplaceable.

94
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:07,700
You’ve been with him since childhood,

95
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:09,420
you’re the most familiar and the dearest to him.

96
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:12,100
You’re his Xinhe who gave birth to his children.

97
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,700
= Zhang Chengzhao =
Excuse me?

98
00:06:55,980 --> 00:06:58,020
Are you looking for Aunt Jia?

99
00:07:01,820 --> 00:07:04,740
Now, outsiders are not accessible to

100
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:06,780
any halls or pavilions.

101
00:07:11,940 --> 00:07:13,140
Thank you.

102
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:14,980
I’m looking for Aunt Jia

103
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:16,780
not for something important.

104
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:19,580
I just haven’t seen her for a while.

105
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:21,380
You’re from the front yard, aren’t you?

106
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:28,220
Was Chief Xia sending you here?

107
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:33,620
I’m Lantiao from Pavilion of Luan.

108
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:36,180
I saw you before,

109
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:39,500
but now,

110
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,260
you can’t get inside.

111
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:45,380
Since you’re here,

112
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:48,380
please help me bring

113
00:07:48,740 --> 00:07:50,980
the folk prescription to Chief Xia?

114
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,380
Folk prescription?

115
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:55,860
It’s popular in the palace

116
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:57,260
these days,

117
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:58,820
which must be great.

118
00:08:04,940 --> 00:08:08,140
= Wang Mansion =

119
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:10,340
I’m not fishing for fame.

120
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:11,860
I’m not!

121
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,020
The Censorate is pursuing justice,

122
00:08:14,260 --> 00:08:16,420
and investigating corrupt officials

123
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:17,940
thoroughly!

124
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:21,260
Darling.

125
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:24,900
What…what are these?

126
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:35,220
Shitty Music Institutes!

127
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:36,940
Profiteering merchants!

128
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:39,300
How dare they defame officials,

129
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:40,780
and disrupt the principles!

130
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:42,020
What’s the Kaifeng Municipal Government doing?

131
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:43,300
Why don’t they arrest those people?

132
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,180
Unruly people!

133
00:08:44,620 --> 00:08:46,660
Come, let’s sue them now!

134
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,020
No.

135
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:51,660
It’s not unruly people or profiteering merchants,

136
00:08:52,300 --> 00:08:53,860
it’s them, it’s them!

137
00:08:54,820 --> 00:08:55,500
Darling.

138
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:58,580
Have a look. It’s official newspaper.

139
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:00,460
Su Shunqin utilized

140
00:09:00,460 --> 00:09:02,060
his power as the chief editor

141
00:09:02,060 --> 00:09:03,660
for personal revenge to humiliate me,

142
00:09:04,500 --> 00:09:06,380
describing my investigation of corruption

143
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:07,980
as colluding with the powerful officials

144
00:09:07,980 --> 00:09:09,020
and persecuting able officials,

145
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:10,380
and describing my risking life to speak out frankly

146
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:12,300
as fishing for fame.

147
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:13,220
He even,

148
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:16,980
even humiliated me with paintings.

149
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:22,140
Darling.

150
00:09:29,540 --> 00:09:30,900
You know what these are?

151
00:09:35,980 --> 00:09:39,340
Are they, are they illustrations of scripts?

152
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:44,340
The official lying on the ground

153
00:09:44,420 --> 00:09:46,660
looks like a dog.

154
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:49,540
This is a folk tabloid

155
00:09:49,540 --> 00:09:51,300
by Su Shunqin.

156
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:54,580
The man lying on the ground like a dog

157
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:56,420
is Deputy Censor Wang Gongchen.

158
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:00,340
What?

159
00:10:01,700 --> 00:10:03,740
How vicious is Su Shunqin!

160
00:10:04,860 --> 00:10:07,140
Wang Gongchen was a young principal graduate

161
00:10:07,700 --> 00:10:08,980
as well as a gifted scholar.

162
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:11,020
A gifted scholar,

163
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:13,660
and an upright gentleman

164
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:16,020
who lied on the ground like a dog

165
00:10:16,020 --> 00:10:16,900
two years ago,

166
00:10:17,420 --> 00:10:19,100
and stopped His Majesty from leaving,

167
00:10:19,380 --> 00:10:20,900
unless His Majesty degraded and cast

168
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:24,020
me out of the Capital.

169
00:10:25,820 --> 00:10:27,860
Before me, their so-called evil villain,

170
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:29,700
they call themselves as gentlemen.

171
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,900
Now, those gentlemen

172
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:35,060
accuse each other of fishing for fame.

173
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:40,420
Look at the newspaper there,

174
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:44,340
Mr. Su accuses Mr. Wang of fishing for fame.

175
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:48,740
Mr. Ouyang boasts that only gentlemen have friends,

176
00:10:50,620 --> 00:10:53,420
blatantly bragging themselves
as a group of gentlemen.

177
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:55,900
Gentlemen are ganging up.

178
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:58,620
Will His Majesty be happy about it?

179
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:01,020
Father!

180
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:05,500
I’ll go and check

181
00:11:05,540 --> 00:11:06,780
what trouble

182
00:11:06,780 --> 00:11:08,220
my son got into?

183
00:11:09,580 --> 00:11:11,860
Father, something goes wrong with the palace.

184
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:14,220
Yang Huaimin couldn’t be contacted for these days.

185
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:15,780
I remembered that

186
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:17,380
you had picked out a eunuch

187
00:11:17,620 --> 00:11:18,780
and promoted him

188
00:11:18,780 --> 00:11:20,020
to be a clerk in the Cabinet.

189
00:11:20,420 --> 00:11:21,340
He is young,

190
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:23,020
and lives with Liang Huaiji,

191
00:11:23,020 --> 00:11:24,820
who served His Majesty.

192
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:26,460
I asked him to

193
00:11:26,460 --> 00:11:27,500
take a look at the backyard,

194
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:30,300
and he did find Lantiao.

195
00:11:40,740 --> 00:11:43,140
Liaozi, did they

196
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:44,940
also wipe out

197
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:45,900
crickets and flying crickets?

198
00:11:47,140 --> 00:11:48,660
There is no chirping now.

199
00:11:50,220 --> 00:11:51,740
There will be in the next year.

200
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:55,940
Okay.

201
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:58,020
Zuixinglai is still young,

202
00:11:58,260 --> 00:11:59,540
so he will still like those creatures next year.

203
00:12:01,460 --> 00:12:02,620
Can you make an insect cage?

204
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:04,540
Yes, Your Majesty.

205
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:06,900
But not very well.

206
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,420
I was taught by my master.

207
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:09,660
He’s skillful.

208
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:11,140
Maoze?

209
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:14,140
he’s clever.

210
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:17,460
He is better than others in many ways.

211
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,300
It’s a pity that a man smart like him

212
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:23,780
was held in the palace since childhood,

213
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:27,500
and couldn’t get the honor of success
in the imperial examination.

214
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:29,620
It must be depressing.

215
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:31,860
Especially

216
00:12:33,860 --> 00:12:35,580
when he is unable to protect the one he loves.

217
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:41,020
Master has been following Your Majesty
at an early age,

218
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:42,500
he is sure to be...

219
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:46,580
He grew up with me,

220
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:49,020
I trust him, and understand him.

221
00:12:54,820 --> 00:12:57,140
He just thinks that the Empress is virtuous.

222
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,700
All of you think that she’s perfect,

223
00:13:00,020 --> 00:13:01,660
and I am not good enough for her.

224
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,260
You put an eye on me for her,

225
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:06,860
to safeguard her position as the Empress.

226
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:13,140
But you fail to realize that

227
00:13:15,380 --> 00:13:16,860
she does not fear me

228
00:13:17,940 --> 00:13:19,980
or lose her position as the Empress.

229
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:22,540
She only fears for

230
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,260
not being a perfect empress.

231
00:13:25,820 --> 00:13:27,660
But no one knows her better than me.

232
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:30,940
She can only be perfect.

233
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:35,100
It is Bihan

234
00:13:35,100 --> 00:13:36,500
who will do something wrong now and then.

235
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,740
You and officials

236
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:41,980
are dying to see Bihan

237
00:13:41,980 --> 00:13:43,020
cause a huge trouble.

238
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:45,500
How can I not take care of her more carefully?

239
00:13:49,420 --> 00:13:51,460
Once Zuixinglai gets well,

240
00:13:52,420 --> 00:13:53,580
he’ll be conferred with the title of crown prince.

241
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:57,020
His study and regular etiquette

242
00:13:57,300 --> 00:13:58,300
will be entrusted to the Empress.

243
00:13:58,980 --> 00:13:59,660
As thus,

244
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:04,660
all of you shall be pleased.

245
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:06,180
and rest assured.

246
00:14:07,340 --> 00:14:08,540
I’ll

247
00:14:09,860 --> 00:14:10,660
be free

248
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:14,820
to spoil him a little privately.

249
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:20,340
Go and fetch the bamboo billet.

250
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,300
Show me how to make an insect cage.

251
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:33,220
Well, forget it. Go and open

252
00:14:33,260 --> 00:14:34,660
the urgent document sent by Fu Bi.

253
00:14:46,220 --> 00:14:50,580
= Xia Mansion =

254
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:06,380
You seem to be very delighted. How come?

255
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:10,300
Could it be that Yan Shu was impeached miserably?

256
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:13,820
How insightful you are!

257
00:15:14,940 --> 00:15:16,700
But he isn’t demoted.

258
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:19,060
I simply seize a chance.

259
00:15:23,020 --> 00:15:26,820
Is it related to the pestilence in the Capital?

260
00:15:29,940 --> 00:15:32,580
Is the pestilence very serious?

261
00:15:33,620 --> 00:15:34,940
The backyard declared

262
00:15:35,340 --> 00:15:36,580
to temporarily ban any maids or eunuchs

263
00:15:36,580 --> 00:15:37,540
from leaving the palace,

264
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:39,300
and those running errands outside

265
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:40,300
cannot return to the palace.

266
00:15:41,700 --> 00:15:44,100
However, Madam Zhang isn’t in good health.

267
00:15:44,300 --> 00:15:45,740
She hasn’t seen me for more than ten days...

268
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:47,300
Let me tell you

269
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:49,900
a top secret that

270
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,900
even Madam Zhang doesn’t know.

271
00:15:54,180 --> 00:15:56,180
Both the Prince and Princess Fukang

272
00:15:56,260 --> 00:15:58,660
are infected with the pestilence.

273
00:16:00,420 --> 00:16:01,180
What?

274
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:03,340
Really?

275
00:16:04,620 --> 00:16:06,180
Of course!

276
00:16:08,020 --> 00:16:10,380
I revealed it to Eighth Prince.

277
00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:12,260
Hearing it, Eighth Prince,

278
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:13,380
who’s sick and fatuous.

279
00:16:13,740 --> 00:16:16,100
attributed it to the retribution that

280
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:18,460
His Majesty recognized a villain as mother.

