557
00:34:07,740 --> 00:34:08,820
Even his current government post

558
00:34:08,820 --> 00:34:10,660
counted on the merit of

559
00:34:10,660 --> 00:34:11,820
late Empress Dowager Zhangyi.

560
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:13,540
And now, he’s too old.

561
00:34:14,220 --> 00:34:15,980
As per the current assessment standards,

562
00:34:16,660 --> 00:34:18,460
he’s on the list of reduction.

563
00:34:19,340 --> 00:34:20,460
All of a sudden,

564
00:34:20,460 --> 00:34:21,940
he became a consultant for no reason.

565
00:34:22,700 --> 00:34:23,820
Isn’t it contempt for

566
00:34:23,820 --> 00:34:25,540
the decree of new policy?

567
00:34:26,220 --> 00:34:29,260
The people must talk about it if they know.

568
00:34:30,460 --> 00:34:32,860
He’s an honest and upright official,

569
00:34:32,940 --> 00:34:34,380
who treats his inferiors
with tolerance and kindness.

570
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:38,420
Li Yonghe has never claimed
any credit for himself,

571
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:41,820
and was cautious with his words and deeds.

572
00:34:42,740 --> 00:34:44,900
Not to mention that he declined promotion
or reward for may times,

573
00:34:45,220 --> 00:34:47,300
and even voluntarily requested resignation.

574
00:34:47,700 --> 00:34:50,380
These merits are his feats.

575
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:53,340
His merits

576
00:34:53,580 --> 00:34:55,140
deserve wealth and rank,

577
00:34:56,100 --> 00:34:57,500
yet no entry to the Cabinet.

578
00:34:58,100 --> 00:35:00,250
Not all officials in the Cabinet

579
00:35:00,300 --> 00:35:01,980
are extraordinary talents.

580
00:35:03,860 --> 00:35:05,620
The Privy Council and the Cabinet

581
00:35:06,180 --> 00:35:07,740
jointly deal with state affairs.

582
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:09,260
Being in want of talents,

583
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:12,100
they shall at least recruit moderately
gifted ones.

584
00:35:14,580 --> 00:35:16,380
Isn’t it your argument that

585
00:35:16,660 --> 00:35:19,300
you used against Empress Dowager
Zhangxian’s personal favor for promotion,

586
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:21,540
when she promoted Zhang Qi,

587
00:35:21,540 --> 00:35:22,900
who she owed a favor?

588
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:28,540
Scholar Ouyang is

589
00:35:28,540 --> 00:35:30,180
a worthy student of Prime Minister Yan.

590
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:32,500
You recite the essay by your respected teacher
so well.

591
00:35:36,380 --> 00:35:37,260
Prime Minister Yan.

592
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:43,980
Ever since the Founding Father established
the final imperial examination,

593
00:35:44,540 --> 00:35:47,260
All students who passed the imperial examination

594
00:35:47,260 --> 00:35:48,860
are students of the Emperor.

595
00:35:49,540 --> 00:35:52,300
Scholar Ouyang and I

596
00:35:52,820 --> 00:35:55,700
are not student and teacher.

597
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:07,220
Prime Minister Yan, you used to,

598
00:36:08,980 --> 00:36:10,940
under great pressure from peer officials,

599
00:36:11,740 --> 00:36:13,060
indignantly and righteously speak up,

600
00:36:14,180 --> 00:36:16,460
accusing Empress Dowager Zhangxian
of abusing grace.

601
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:18,300
To return the favor of offering shelter
in early day,

602
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:19,900
she gave Zhang Qi, an incompetent official,

603
00:36:20,020 --> 00:36:22,580
not only wealth and position, but also power,

604
00:36:22,580 --> 00:36:23,940
which greatly damaged the laws and principles.

605
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:25,340
Prime Minister Yan.

606
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:29,100
How righteous you were sixteen years ago.

607
00:36:30,300 --> 00:36:31,820
Now that you are a prime minister,

608
00:36:33,740 --> 00:36:34,740
and you’ve changed?

609
00:36:36,900 --> 00:36:38,820
Scholar Ouyang, you’re wrong again.

610
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:42,100
During Empress Dowager Zhangxian’s dictatorship,

611
00:36:42,700 --> 00:36:44,900
Prime Minister Yan defied her

612
00:36:44,900 --> 00:36:46,780
to pledge loyalty to His Majesty.

613
00:36:47,820 --> 00:36:50,340
But this decree was His Majesty’s will,

614
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:53,420
Prime Minister Yan remained loyal to His Majesty.

615
00:36:53,460 --> 00:36:54,340
I reckon that

616
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:56,740
His Majesty owns the country,

617
00:36:56,740 --> 00:36:57,980
and also shoulders responsibilities.

618
00:36:59,020 --> 00:37:00,340
His Majesty owns the nation,

619
00:37:00,500 --> 00:37:01,860
and also bears its weight.

620
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:04,100
Whatever policy that is harmful to the nation,

621
00:37:04,100 --> 00:37:05,380
no matter who proposes,

622
00:37:05,580 --> 00:37:07,780
shall be objected.

623
00:37:08,540 --> 00:37:11,020
Being loyal to the nation is great loyalty,

624
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:12,900
Being loyal to His Majesty’s country

625
00:37:13,100 --> 00:37:15,780
is true loyalty to His Majesty.

626
00:37:17,500 --> 00:37:19,460
Scholar Ouyang,
you’re an official of the Remonstrance Bureau.

627
00:37:20,380 --> 00:37:22,820
If you have any disagreement with the deeds
of the Cabinet or the Privy Council,

628
00:37:22,820 --> 00:37:25,700
you can come directly
to His Majesty for impeachment.

629
00:37:26,180 --> 00:37:28,740
But you come here and argue with me privately.

630
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:31,380
It’s improper.

631
00:37:42,180 --> 00:37:44,460
Reports from Jingji Province
and Jingdong West Province

632
00:37:44,460 --> 00:37:45,660
said that

633
00:37:46,420 --> 00:37:48,940
the pestilence was discovered at an early stage

634
00:37:49,180 --> 00:37:50,140
without further spreading.

635
00:37:51,220 --> 00:37:53,620
But there are many victims of floods

636
00:37:53,620 --> 00:37:54,820
who scatter to many counties.

637
00:37:56,100 --> 00:37:59,500
We shall prevent the risk of pestilence outbreaks,

638
00:37:59,620 --> 00:38:03,540
and also prevent those victims from turning
to robbers or bandits

639
00:38:04,020 --> 00:38:05,060
in lack of livelihood.

640
00:38:07,180 --> 00:38:08,020
Prime Minister Jia,

641
00:38:10,300 --> 00:38:11,020
Prime Minister Jia!

642
00:38:14,020 --> 00:38:16,900
Loyalty is the duty of an official,

643
00:38:17,140 --> 00:38:19,860
I shall at His Majesty’s service.

644
00:38:23,660 --> 00:38:25,220
What you mentioned

645
00:38:25,380 --> 00:38:27,540
is the most important principle.

646
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:31,540
Then, how to deal with

647
00:38:31,900 --> 00:38:34,500
the victims of Jingji Province
and Jingdong West Province?

648
00:38:35,060 --> 00:38:35,780
Well…

649
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:39,380
His Majesty is wise enough to make a decision.

650
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:32,700
Father, I’ve finished five spoons.

651
00:39:32,940 --> 00:39:33,860
I want a candied fruit.

652
00:39:36,740 --> 00:39:39,420
Do you think that I’m too old
to see things clearly,

653
00:39:39,780 --> 00:39:40,820
or to count?

654
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:42,860
You missed one spoon.

655
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:47,100
Well, I must be too sick

656
00:39:47,260 --> 00:39:48,380
to count.

657
00:39:49,060 --> 00:39:50,860
Father, please, have pity on

658
00:39:51,300 --> 00:39:53,380
silly Huirou by giving one more candied fruit.

659
00:40:06,620 --> 00:40:07,780
Have two more spoons of porridge

660
00:40:08,900 --> 00:40:09,940
after you eat this candied fruit.

661
00:40:16,020 --> 00:40:16,660
Here you are.

662
00:40:34,620 --> 00:40:36,420
Father, I feel good.

663
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:37,900
You can leave and take a rest.

664
00:40:38,420 --> 00:40:39,900
Huaiji will stay with me.

665
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:41,300
And I shall fear nothing.

666
00:40:44,220 --> 00:40:45,220
Having Huaiji here,

667
00:40:46,500 --> 00:40:47,780
then you don’t need my company.

668
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:58,580
Father, your cheek has sunken,

669
00:40:59,380 --> 00:41:01,020
and you have dark circles around eyes.

670
00:41:02,060 --> 00:41:03,940
If you don’t take a rest,

671
00:41:04,620 --> 00:41:07,460
what if you get sick?

672
00:41:18,060 --> 00:41:19,140
Don’t worry, father.

673
00:41:19,660 --> 00:41:20,940
I will be a good girl.

674
00:41:21,420 --> 00:41:24,060
I’ll take medicine and have meals.

675
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:26,060
When I recover,

676
00:41:26,660 --> 00:41:28,300
I’ll take care of mother.

677
00:41:29,700 --> 00:41:31,100
Father, you can entrust mother

678
00:41:31,420 --> 00:41:32,780
to me.

679
00:41:38,940 --> 00:41:39,620
Fine.

680
00:41:41,740 --> 00:41:42,580
Fine.

681
00:41:44,420 --> 00:41:47,580
Huirou has grown up and is a competent girl.

682
00:41:49,420 --> 00:41:52,220
I’ll entrust your mother to you.

683
00:41:53,900 --> 00:41:55,100
Promise to keep a good company with her.

684
00:41:56,380 --> 00:41:57,540
And don’t make her…

685
00:42:01,500 --> 00:42:02,540
Don’t let her grieve.

686
00:42:21,780 --> 00:42:31,460
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

687
00:42:32,780 --> 00:42:41,140
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

688
00:42:43,980 --> 00:42:48,700
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

689
00:42:49,660 --> 00:42:53,820
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

690
00:42:55,260 --> 00:43:00,740
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

691
00:43:00,740 --> 00:43:05,540
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

692
00:43:09,220 --> 00:43:14,860
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

693
00:43:14,860 --> 00:43:19,740
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

694
00:43:20,260 --> 00:43:26,020
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

695
00:43:26,020 --> 00:43:31,100
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

696
00:43:31,540 --> 00:43:36,460
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

697
00:43:37,100 --> 00:43:41,940
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

698
00:43:42,620 --> 00:43:47,780
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

699
00:43:48,260 --> 00:43:53,300
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

700
00:43:53,860 --> 00:43:57,940
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

701
00:43:59,380 --> 00:44:04,020
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

702
00:44:05,060 --> 00:44:10,220
♪ The howling wind ♪

703
00:44:10,580 --> 00:44:14,660
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

704
00:44:16,140 --> 00:44:21,060
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

705
00:44:21,700 --> 00:44:26,940
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

706
00:44:27,340 --> 00:44:32,620
♪ The howling wind ♪

707
00:44:32,940 --> 00:44:37,820
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

708
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:45,140
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
